net.ognyanov.niogram.parser

Interface AstParser

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ErrorDispatcher
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Antlr4AstParser

    public interface AstParser
extends ErrorDispatcher
    A common interface for translators from grammar specification languages to the NioGram AST.

    So far mostly a placeholder because there is only one supported grammar specification language - ANTLR 4.

    Author:
    Nikolay Ognyanov
